RenoiseScriptingTool.Name: EggSemm FastTracker Exporter
RenoiseScriptingTool.Author: aldroid
RenoiseScriptingTool.Description: Exports FastTracker XM files. It's pre-alpha quality, but it is cross-platform, simple to use, and has no extra dependencies. You WILL need to process your files in a proper FastTracker-capable tracker after use.
